condition.narrative: Finance Agreement: Audited Financial Statements |Description: The Recipient shall have its Financial Statements audited for theperiod of one fiscal year not later than six (6) months after the end of such period |Frequency: Yearly

Finance Agreement: External Auditing firm |Description: The Recipient shall appoint not later than three (3) months aftereffectiveness Deadline, an external auditing firm acceptable to the Association in accordance with Section III.C of Schedule 2 |Frequency: Yearly

Finance Agreement: Financial management system |Description: Establish not later than three (3) months after the EffectivenessDeadline, and thereafter maintain a financial management system (including related staff, software and internal auditor) |Frequency: Yearly

Finance Agreement: Interim unaudited financial reports |Description: Furnish to the Association not later than forty five (45) daysafter the end of each calendar quarter, interim unaudited financial reports for the Project covering the quarter | Frequency:Quarterly
